# Prevent host dependencies and build artifacts from inflating the Docker build context
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/.astro
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/.cache

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
.DS_Store

# Git metadata should stay outside the image
.git

